@startuml
title Prometheus Monitoring System - Control Flow

actor User
participant "Sample Node.js App" as App
participant "prom-client Library" as PromClient
participant "Prometheus Server" as Prometheus
participant "Alertmanager" as Alertmanager
participant "Grafana" as Grafana

== Application Startup ==
User -> App: Start Application
activate App
App -> PromClient: Initialize metrics\n(summaries, histograms)
activate PromClient
PromClient --> App: Metrics initialized
deactivate PromClient
App --> User: Application running\non HTTP server
deactivate App

== Metric Collection ==
User -> App: HTTP Request
activate App
App -> PromClient: Record request start
activate PromClient
App -> App: Process request\n(simulate latency)
App -> PromClient: Record request duration
PromClient -> PromClient: Update summary\nand histogram metrics
PromClient --> App: Metrics updated
deactivate PromClient
App --> User: HTTP Response
deactivate App

== Prometheus Scraping (Pull-Based) ==
Prometheus -> Prometheus: Scrape interval triggered\n(configured in prometheus.yml)
activate Prometheus
Prometheus -> App: GET /metrics
activate App
App -> PromClient: Generate metrics output
activate PromClient
PromClient --> App: Prometheus format metrics
deactivate PromClient
App --> Prometheus: Metrics data
deactivate App
Prometheus -> Prometheus: Store metrics in\ntime-series database
deactivate Prometheus

== Alert Evaluation ==
Prometheus -> Prometheus: Evaluate alert rules\n(prometheus.rules.yml)
activate Prometheus
Prometheus -> Prometheus: Rule conditions met?
alt Alert condition triggered
    Prometheus -> Alertmanager: Send alert
    activate Alertmanager
    Alertmanager -> Alertmanager: Deduplicate and\ngroup alerts
    Alertmanager -> Alertmanager: Route alert based\non configuration
    Alertmanager --> Prometheus: Alert received
    deactivate Alertmanager
end
deactivate Prometheus

== Visualization ==
User -> Grafana: Access dashboard
activate Grafana
Grafana -> Prometheus: Query metrics\n(PromQL query)
activate Prometheus
Prometheus -> Prometheus: Retrieve time-series data
Prometheus --> Grafana: Query results
deactivate Prometheus
Grafana -> Grafana: Render dashboard\nvisualization
Grafana --> User: Display metrics dashboard
deactivate Grafana

== SLO/Error Budget Monitoring ==
User -> Grafana: View SLO dashboard
activate Grafana
Grafana -> Prometheus: Query error budget\nand burn rate
activate Prometheus
Prometheus -> Prometheus: Calculate SLO metrics\nfrom existing data
Prometheus --> Grafana: SLO calculation results
deactivate Prometheus
Grafana --> User: Display SLO metrics
deactivate Grafana

@enduml
